. For each
{jjdhr_heat}
(all statuses: racing, stabled, retired):
.. For each
{jjdpr_pace}
in
{jjdhm_order}:
... If `--actionable` specified, skip paces not in
{jjdpe_rough}
or
{jjdpe_bridled}
state
... Search in order (first match wins):
.... {jjdkm_silks}
(from `tacks[0].silks`)
.... {jjdkm_text}
(spec from `tacks[0].text`)
.... {jjdkm_direction}
(from `tacks[0].direction` if present)
.... {jjdhm_paddock}
file content
